Ultra Magnus sent a comm back. "We do my friend  but it is all not bad. 
Prime's body as been discovered on Cybertron. It was held captive by the 
predacons there. The Maximals have been able to find  its resting place and 
are raging an assault to recapture it. The Tripreds have destroyed much of 
our former strength im afraid. Our chance of rescuing him seems slim.  I 
myself ended up here because I had no other choice. I was escaping tripred  
ships. The Tripred General  on cybertron known as Blackheart is incredibly 
strong."

--part1_115.1911bc60.2ada4418_boundary
